{"tid":1233671,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"會員三毛評級機制","createTime":"2019-06-16T20:16:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T02:59:20.000Z","uid":255347,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0f9349141f34b98f0750422cc6136d372e80c0e8","tid":1233671,"uid":255347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:16:50.000Z","msg":"鑑於連登三毛日益氾濫<br />\n連仔會唔會考慮整返個會員三毛評級系統？<br />\n<br />\n例如：<br />\n草夠5000粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=好可能係三毛 (個名隔離會有標示，限制開post)<br />\n草夠10000粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=確認係三毛 (完全禁言）<br />\n<br />\n同時設有平反機制<br />\n草夠10000粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可平反<br />\n<br />\n以杜絕三毛 同時減少誤判"},{"pid":"8f2d3f31d0f63a5af1eae72396ae77ba122fe3a8","tid":1233671,"uid":159444,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:36:57.000Z","msg":"好重要，大家留意，真心！求大家最少睇第一個post<br />\n<br />\n呢場仗要小心打！我覺得呢位巴打分析得好到位！<br />\n<br />\n[文長，文宣]分析中央打法已經開始由明轉暗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1233323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1233323</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n為防被抹黑 同商討下一步行動 我建議揾民陣宣佈&quot;暫休&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1233591\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1233591</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"00b6807f0073d7309964bc49e278eb62f4c18910","tid":1233671,"uid":164313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:37:28.000Z","msg":"希望每一位兄弟、手足，做每一件事之前 諗清楚成效 後果<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1233588\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1233588</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"33a90e60d7ee6cc3a1ebb2a7f92804d91ee25612","tid":1233671,"uid":261343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T22:49:39.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"764b95327dc99da08b5509d966cd38a4fece1281","tid":1233671,"uid":255347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33a90e60d7ee6cc3a1ebb2a7f92804d91ee25612","tid":1233671,"